Author:
Vol / Page:  2
Edition:
Quote:  Of native shrubs, I noticed howhi, kowhai, ngutu-kaka, koromiko, and manuka, as well as the pretty turutu (<i>dianella intrmedia</i>) and cocksfoot grass, hawkweed, sowthistle, and wild geranium.
